task.summary: Default task
Fixed Aggregate UI to look like new UI
Fixed errant background by enforcing null background on updateCover before a cover is searched for.
Some UI tweaking
Removed = and * from comment dialogas of questionable use
Fixed an issue that meant different views didn't lanuch on data views when choosing from context button.
Added checking of cache in VhReviewAbstract before binding
Added checking of cache in VhReviewAbstract before binding
Added caching for profile image in VhReviewAbstract and CacheVhNode
Added profile images to feed screen

Fixed bug in ReviewOptionsSelector that didn't set mInitialised to false when authorId was set.
Changed selected cell colour in publish screen.
Changed CacheVhNode to always update cache even if same reviewId.

Simplified Review repo hierarchy:
Removed LocalRepository. ReferencesRepository name changed to ReviewRepository. This now has getReview as well as GteReference etc. Mutable extends from ReviewsRepository.
ReviewsRepository name changed to ReviewsSource. ReviewsSource changed name to NodeRepository.
Removed getBookmarks from MutableRepository and put in ReviewsRepository.
Moved bookmark reference for ReviewCollection up to UI level.
Changed xRepository to xRepo
Some renaming to make it easier to read for Backend API prep
Some renaming to make it easier to read for Backend API prep
Some renaming to make it easier to read for Backend API prep
Some refactoring of PersistencePlugin stuff to make it easier to navigate and read
Changed SortableListImpl.sort(comparator) to no longer reference Collections.sort
Changed SortableListImpl.sort(comparator) to no longer reference Collections.sort

Changed edit screens to use "Done" contextual button instead of tick in menu to confirm edits.
Average of criteria menu button in review build screen only shows for full mode.
Made subject edit text bigger, hint colour lighter and cursor thicker.
Made subject edit text bigger, hint colour lighter and cursor thicker.
Changed MyGeneralLibrary to CoreLibrary
Changed Reviewer to Startouch and changed relevant package name
Deleted old Reviewer.iml and commented out some code in AppInstanceAndroid
Changed Google Places API key in manifest to get it working again with the new package name.
Update LocationClientGoogle to replace deprecated FusedLocationApi with FusedLocationClient

Added TitleDecorator classs to help make clickable buttons more obvious by decorating them with "/" or "-" dependning on purpose.
Changed "Distribution" to "Buckets".
Updated the Readme.md files
Changed package name mygenerallibray to corelibray

In the process of adding a profile page.
Refactored AuthorProfileRef and SocialProfile as not quite fir for this purpose.
Fixed some bugs in the last commit
Changed ListReference so that is can give a size reference too. This simplifies binding to just the size.
Refactored ReviewSubscriber system as too much like reference binder so merged the two.
Fixed bug in RepoCollection that was casing nested calls for dereferencing when firing for binder.
Made profile page place to follow, unfollow and edit profiles. Removed MaiFollow form review list page.
Fixed bug in ActivityProfile that wasn't setting activity in app onResume.
Changed AdapterNodeFollowablw to AdapterReviewsList and removed followId stuff
Moved DataReference stuff to CoreLibrary
Some code cleanup
Some code cleanup
Some code cleanup
Removed delay task in ReviewNodeRepo
Some cleaning and refactoring of FragmentAuthorView plus some moving around of UiManagers
Merged Dev with master
Some code cleanup
Some code cleanup
Some code cleanup
Fixed crash that was happening after resuming after a long period of time.
